Text.Value: We will... Absolute will rule all...
Where did you start following the Absolute?
Who killed you?
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Moonrise Towers... initiation...
Scouting... found druids...
No...
Who are you?
Your name and House. Now.
Druid... Bear...
Leave.
Ned'Cirannis... of the Absolute...
No houses... all equal in Her love...
There is no House of the Absolute.
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Text.Value: Where did you get your tadpole?

Synopsis: A drow heading a scouting party was killed by Halsin in bear form. The drow was tadpoled, like the player, but unlike the player he has no idea he was infected. He thinks the tadpole was the voice of his god - the Absolute - speaking to him.
